    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 1 against a required level of 2 due to single-condition testing; this gap is accepted given the direct correspondence of the test condition to the regulatory COU and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level conclusion. FEA predictions satisfy all pre-specified acceptance criteria for the three QoIs.",
